WEBVTT

00:13:30.640 --> 00:13:32.936
At the end of the evening this year,

00:13:32.960 --> 00:13:36.640
one of our young,
delightful teenaged girls,

00:13:37.680 --> 00:13:40.000
Caitlin, said to her mom,

00:13:41.640 --> 00:13:44.456
"That was the best night
of my whole life."

00:13:44.480 --> 00:13:46.856
And that's just the point,

00:13:46.880 --> 00:13:50.616
to capture the best days and nights,

00:13:50.640 --> 00:13:52.720
to abolish limitations,

00:13:53.520 --> 00:13:55.656
to have your default answer be "yes"

00:13:55.680 --> 00:13:58.720
and your default question be, "Why not?"

00:13:59.800 --> 00:14:02.296
Ultimately life is too short,